<D>__{what's this fool playin at?}
<A>__{maceo isn't going to wait to find out. he grabs the wires with both hands, yanks they hold firm! he looks to the stage, panicked as sonny brings his fingers to the strings and the amp blasts the room with a long, trip hammering, spine shivering, electric guitar intro! ty stands at the piano with his mouth hanging open sonny whoops and leans into his microphone }
